OL,3,CLegacy Funeral Directors: Hull Funeral
OL,4,Chome could be turned into car garage
OL,6,FA planning application has been
OL,7,Fsubmitted to convert a Hull Funeral
OL,8,FHome which is under investigation into
OL,9,Fa car repair garage.
OL,11,FThe application to convert the Hessle
OL,12,FRoad site has been validated by Hull
OL,13,FCity Council and will now enter
OL,14,Fconsultation process before a decision
OL,15,Fon the site's future is made.
OL,17,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors
OL,18,Fown three sites in East Yorkshire, two
OL,19,Fin Hull and one in Beverley.
