OL,3,CLegacy Funeral Directors: Hull Funeral
OL,4,Chome could be turned into car garage
OL,6,FIn March, Humberside Police descended
OL,7,Fon its base in Hessle Road after they
OL,8,Freceived concerns over care for the
OL,9,Fdeceased.
OL,11,FOfficers seized 35 bodies and a
OL,12,Fquantity of human ashes linked to a
OL,13,Ffurther 163 families in the region.
OL,15,FA 46-year-old man and a 23-year old
OL,16,Fwoman were arrested in March on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of prevention of lawful and
OL,18,Fdecent burial and fraud offences.
