OL,6,FIn an update issued on Thursday, 12
OL,7,FDecember, police confirmed the 23-year-
OL,8,Fold woman is longer a suspect.
OL,10,FThe man remains on conditional police
OL,11,Fbail, along with a 54-year-old woman
OL,12,Farrested in July on suspicion of money
OL,13,Flaundering.
OL,15,FHull City Council and East Riding
OL,16,FCouncil have since committed to
OL,17,Festablishing a permanent memorial for
OL,18,Fthose affected by the incident.
