OL,7,Fbeen home to Heavenly Services,
OL,8,Fanother funeral service provider,
OL,9,Fwhich was also investigated by
OL,10,FHumberside Police before collapsing in
OL,11,F2021.
OL,13,FHull City Council are accepting
OL,14,Fcomments on the submitted plans to
OL,15,Fconvert the site into a car garage on
OL,16,Fthe council website.
